headline: Eastman Announces 2025 Annual Meeting Stockholder Vote Results
summary: KINGSPORT, Tenn., May 01, 2025--Eastman Chemical Company (NYSE:EMN) announced its 2025 Annual Meeting stockholder vote results.

headline: Eastman Board Declares Dividend
summary: KINGSPORT, Tenn., May 01, 2025--The Board of Directors of Eastman Chemical Company (NYSE:EMN) has declared a quarterly cash dividend of $0.83 per share on the company's common stock.
